{"tid":2311261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊︱庭上播廣明苑閉路電視片段 顯示一團黑衣墜落 附近沒有他人","createTime":"2020-12-04T02:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T09:54:32.000Z","uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"761fec1757a4ae471d62ee667c450316f12cb101","tid":2311261,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"科大男生周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突中，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲。死因庭就事件昨進行研訊至第14天，死因裁判官高偉雄突指翻看廣明苑閉路電視片段後，看到之前未見過、而且「非常關鍵」的新細節，故需重新檢視全部閉路電視片段，確保調查齊全及準確。法庭今播放當晚廣明苑閉路電視片段，高官提醒陪審團及周父母，稱片段可能會引起不安。<br />\n<br />\n片段所見，拍得涉案停車場有一團黑衣墜落，附近沒有煙、沒有槍炮，亦沒有其他人。"},{"pid":"170e263abb47d6d2185bb3cc930b0f8693735382","tid":2311261,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/YSRDWIBSXFC2VB7KULT3AYLY6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FYSRDWIBSXFC2VB7KULT3AYLY6M%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=87f3d2eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FYSRDWIBSXFC2VB7KULT3AYLY6M%2F&h=9d860a02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/YSRDWIBSXFC2VB7KULT3AYLY6M/</a>"},{"pid":"ae3b1fe04ca9c8217add1b9a280a11f74ba88f10","tid":2311261,"uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"有一團黑衣墜落，附近沒有煙、沒有槍炮，亦沒有其他人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解釋醫生話佢跌落去既時候已經冇知覺"},{"pid":"041782edf62422ca2f14a52aaed522bc168b3b78","tid":2311261,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ae3b1fe04ca9c8217add1b9a280a11f74ba88f10","tid":2311261,"uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"有一團黑衣墜落，附近沒有煙、沒有槍炮，亦沒有其他人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解釋醫生話佢跌落去既時候已經冇知覺"},"c